Tetapi Qian Yuan belajar begitu cepat,

00:16:59.680 --> 00:17:00.720
yang bermaksud di mahkamah,

00:17:00.880 --> 00:17:02.280
terdapat mata-mata Qian Yuan.

00:17:03.960 --> 00:17:04.600
Menteri kiri.

